input_str: Title: Subzero Peak Creator: VoltJolt112 Type: FFA / Team We picked this map for it’s look-and-feel and design. This map simulates a sort of frozen valley, situated in the middle of a few mountains, and with a cliff in the middle of it. It reminds us a bit of those winter resorts. The map itself isn’t too big, so you can play it with small and big groups, and it offers many places to hide,
